window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Wyverns, Demons, and an upcoming apocalypse.</b></p> <p>After the death of Mori Gladius, the champion of the human lands, humankind is still reeling. Belzu is on the run, and Levithus has the Sword of Alexander. With Salvos finally reunited with her companions, perhaps... this is the perfect chance to deal with one of her problems once and for all.</p>"; 
